{"0":"Everything is complete and correct. Here's a summary of what was accomplished:\n\n---\n\n## 任务完成总结\n\n### 1. 文件重命名 ✅\n- 从 65 个 PDF 文件的**页面内容**（而非元数据，因为元数据与实际内容不匹配）中提取了真实标题\n- 将空格和斜杠替换为下划线，生成合法文件名\n- 65 个文件已复制到 `/tmp_workspace/results/papers/`（扁平结构）\n- 重命名映射表已写入 `paper_digest.md`\n\n**关键发现**：这批 PDF 的元数据（`title` 字段）与页面实际内容不匹配——元数据来自完全不同的论文，因此使用字体大小启发式方法从页面文本中提取了真实标题。\n\n### 2. 论文分类 ✅\n65 篇论文分类结果：\n- **Multimodal / Vision-Language Models**: 19 篇\n- **Medical Image Analysis**: 7 篇  \n- **Image / Video Generation & Editing**: 15 篇\n- **Autonomous Driving / Robotics / Embodied AI**: 9 篇\n- **3D Vision / Reconstruction / Gaussian Splatting**: 7 篇\n- **Others**: 8 篇\n\n### 3. Caption 相关论文与表格提取 ✅\n找到 **2 篇** image caption 相关论文：\n1. **CAPRL: STIMULATING DENSE IMAGE CAPTION CAPABILITIES VIA REINFORCEMENT LEARNING** — 核心专注于密集图像描述生成的强化学习方法，提取了其 Table 2（图像来源消融实验）\n2. **Asymmetric Idiosyncrasies in Multimodal Models** — 研究不同 captioning 模型的风格指纹，提取了其 Table 2（各模型最具区分性的 TF-IDF 短语）\n\n所有结果已保存到 `/tmp_workspace/results/paper_digest.md`。","_meta":{"runtime":"node","runtimeVersion":"22.22.1","hostname":"170148a3a6f8","name":"openclaw","date":"2026-06-27T15:32:03.783Z","logLevelId":3,"logLevelName":"INFO","path":{"fullFilePath":"file:///usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-DVwhOlEq.js:975:46","fileName":"subsystem-DVwhOlEq.js","fileNameWithLine":"subsystem-DVwhOlEq.js:975","fileColumn":"46","fileLine":"975","filePath":"/usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-DVwhOlEq.js","filePathWithLine":"/usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-DVwhOlEq.js:975","method":"console.log"}},"time":"2026-06-27T15:32:03.783+00:00"}
